{"tid":1478551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中宣部8.18北京天安門集會 聲援香港","createTime":"2019-08-16T14:31:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T15:12:17.000Z","uid":184679,"like":74,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"3d266c6aa8686f1c63f45ae7b65dd725481eecb8","tid":1478551,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:31:11.000Z","msg":"香港人民的反送中運動震動世界，8月18日香港民眾將再次舉行大遊行。而中共宣傳部門日前宣佈也將在18日主辦活動，成龍將在當天成為天安門廣場上的「領頭護旗手」，此言一出，引發民眾對成龍的譏諷。<br />\n<br />\n幾個中共官媒聯合主辦的活動宣傳中寫道，18日港星成龍將作為「領頭護旗手」帶領大陸民眾站上天安門廣場進行所謂的「聲援」香港，「你是跟我一樣的護旗手嗎？是就請跟我來廣場！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2019-08-16/5168766\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.epochtimes.com%2Fnews%2F2019-08-16%2F5168766&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0YgmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=24f880e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2019-08-16/5168766</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/1565838925-53fd16e8f6905a2ee79152166204a998-1024x579.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2F1565838925-53fd16e8f6905a2ee79152166204a998-1024x579.jpg&h=9d31a604&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"423c7bdd8fa2dbefafc613c5ae6d6a81b3fa5acd","tid":1478551,"uid":52828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:34:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c7b460d7ea4b0ecd57821d20a81c81074c12c405","tid":1478551,"uid":12171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:37:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b4929bec4f2721971906dbf17dd54c99efb89bd","tid":1478551,"uid":51798,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:38:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nCFQ5jL.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http